    "description": "step into the world of dysto-wanderer, a captivating 3d puzzle adventure set in a desolate post-apocalyptic landscape. play as Pia, a young girl who wakes up in the toxic slums of a ruined city with no memory of what happened. feeling lost and disoriented, she embarks on a journey to find safety and, if there are any, other survivors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/d4cc92611f2cc74f9c9d112dc3b3d02b.poster.avif?t=1767699364\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/d4cc92611f2cc74f9c9d112dc3b3d02b.webm?t=1767699364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/d4cc92611f2cc74f9c9d112dc3b3d02b.mp4?t=1767699364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/3931c7bd6624ba405de430e1fed07477.avif?t=1767699364\" width=617 height=80 /></span><br>dysto-wanderer offers a unique blend of exploration, puzzle-solving, and survival. every corner holds a new challenge, and each solved puzzle reveals another piece of the story. will you help Pia find her way in this fractured world? join her journey and uncover the mysteries that await in dysto-wanderer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/086aaf0f65a421a1fc9b04e8b54c29b5.poster.avif?t=1767699364\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/086aaf0f65a421a1fc9b04e8b54c29b5.webm?t=1767699364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/086aaf0f65a421a1fc9b04e8b54c29b5.mp4?t=1767699364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/b6f1cae9d3d2cc372b5a77d7945a6372.avif?t=1767699364\" width=603 height=80 /></span><br>navigate through a variety of challenging environments, including toxic city slums, abandoned escape tunnel, overgrown dump, and misty cave. each location offers unique puzzles that require you to hack retro computer terminals, decrypt old ciphers, or solve other intricate quests. as you progress, uncover the secrets of a destroyed civilization and piece together the story of its downfall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/5a8701b4ff41b187f9707b73a44960b3.poster.avif?t=1767699364\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/5a8701b4ff41b187f9707b73a44960b3.webm?t=1767699364\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/5a8701b4ff41b187f9707b73a44960b3.mp4?t=1767699364\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/3adb3851a524ddbad395530f0ff653d5.avif?t=1767699364\" width=584 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/07f031be0ef6ee917e56a27d56cbea2e.poster.avif?t=1767699364\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113420/extras/07f031be0ef6ee91